</p>
<p>That's a little shortcut to get that <code>use</code> statement you always need for validation.</p>
<p>Now, above <code>username</code>, add <code>@Assert\NotBlank</code> with a <code>message</code> option. Go back and
copy the clever message and paste it here:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="c0149566a5">
