<h2 id="handling-validation-in-the-controller">Handling Validation in the Controller <a class="headerlink" href="validation-errors-response#handling-validation-in-the-controller" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Ok! That was step 1. Step 2 is to go into the controller and send the validation
errors back to the user. We're using forms, so handling validation is going to look
pretty much identical to how it looks in traditional web forms.</p>
